Add this snippet to the `page.php` file, usually just before the `</article>` tag:

~~~ .php
<p><?php static::share(); ?></p>
~~~

Open `.\lot\extend\plugin\lot\share\lot\state\config.php` to configure:

~~~ .php
[
    'counter' => true, // Enable sharing counter?
    'list' => ['facebook', 'twitter'],
    'style' => ['color'] // Modify the social sharing button(s) appearance
]
~~~

### Modifier

Modifier for the `style` property:

 - `color`
 - `icon`
 - `round`

